snippet.title: Terrahawks (Videopac G7000/Odyssey²)[#51]
snippet.description:
Another one of the better games for the Videopac. 
This is also a '+' enhanced cartridge, which means there would be a high resolution background image in the background if you play this cartridge in a G7400 console. 
Nothing added to the gameplay afaik.
Maybe I'll show the '+' version once I have more cartridges and/or a flash-/multicart.
This is the final Videopac video so far because I don't have any more games for it at the moment.
